high_descs: Cross the room and go right and then turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and take the pot out of the top of the fridge and then shut the door.
Go left and turn to face the sink.
Put the pot in the sink and turn the water on and then off and then pick the pot up again.
Turn around and cross the room and then turn right to face the shelves.
Put the pot on the right side of the shelf second from the bottom.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pot on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn to your right then walk forward then turn right head to the fridge on your left
Open the fridge pick up the dirty pot then close the fridge
Turn left then walk straight then turn to your right face the sink
Put the pot in the sink, rinse it and fill up with water
Pick up the pot with water then turn to your left walk straight, then face the shelf rack on your right
Put the pot with water on the shelf rack
anns.task_desc: Put the pot with water on the shelf rack

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the fridge on the left.
Open the freezer door, take the pot out of the freezer, close the door.
Turn left and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the pot in the sink, fill the pot with water, pick up the pot.
Turn left and walk to the shelves on the right that are to the left of the end of the counter.
Place the pot down on the right side of the second shelf.
anns.task_desc: To fill a pot with water and place the pot on the shelf.
